text: Frank Phillipson was a male athlete who competed for England. ==Athletics career== He competed for England in the pole vault at the 1934 British Empire Games in London. Phillipson represented Salford Harriers and was the 1934 AAA champion. ==References== Category:English male pole vaulters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1934 British Empire Games
title: Frank Phillipson
